#Text=Live in a World Full of Preconceptions
#Text=Your family , your neighbors , everybody has these preconceptions .
#Text=You might ask yourself , " How should I behave ? "
#Text=" What clothes should I wear ? "
#Text=" Who should I be like ? "
#Text=" How much should I score ? "
#Text=" Which college should I go to ? "
#Text=and so on and so forth .
#Text=But now , you have decided that you are done with thinking about these questions .
#Text=You want to live free .
#Text=You want to learn to appreciate the small things in life .
#Text=You want to be madly in love with life .
#Text=If this describes what you want , then this wikiHow will help teach you how to live in a world full of preconceptions .
#Text=Steps
#Text=Have a cause for hope , or a reason to live .
#Text=Have something to look forward to .
#Text=It might be to travel the world , or buy a motorcycle and ride cross country , or maybe you want to learn about different cultures .
#Text=Find beauty in the most odd and imperfect things - from an old , wrinkle faced woman bent over a fire , to a tiny flower growing on a hillside .
#Text=Learn to calm down .
#Text=Take it in from one ear and let it out through the other .
#Text=These days , you do n't really see anyone who is not willing to get into a fight .
#Text=When you get stuck in an argument , take a deep breath .
#Text=Listen to what the other person has to say .
#Text=Think it through .
#Text=Ask yourself : does what they said make sense ?
#Text=Are they correct ?
#Text=Are you wrong ?
#Text=If you do find sense in what they say , let them know .
#Text=Accept your fault .
#Text=If you find yourself to be the correct one , then do n't yell to make your point .
#Text=Be calm .
#Text=Explain your view to the person .
#Text=If they refuse to understand , hope that they eventually will .
#Text=Be understanding .
#Text=Understand one another , understand the needs of others , and understand the complications in the matter .
#Text=See the situation through the other person 's point of view .
#Text=Just this one step would make you a happy person .
#Text=But do n't be disappointed if the other person fails to show understanding for your matter .
#Text=Not everyone is like you .
#Text=Live free .
#Text=Break society 's rules .
#Text=If your elders tell you that it 's unladylike to wear shorts , do n't listen .
#Text=People will always tell you what to do and what not to do because they all consider themselves better than others , and they think that their ideas and what they think is what is correct .
#Text=Despair not , for that should not bother you .
#Text=You are the maker of decisions your life .
#Text=You can do what you love to do and what you know is right .
#Text=Remember that no one is broken too bad .
#Text=There 's always that glue to fix you up .
#Text=Your job is to find that glue .
